# Gmail
IMAPAccount gmail-private
Host imap.gmail.com
Port 993
UserCmd "decget \"$(xdg-user-dir DOCUMENTS)/accounts/gmail-private.gpg\" user"
PassCmd "decget \"$(xdg-user-dir DOCUMENTS)/accounts/gmail-private.gpg\" app-password"
TLSType IMAPS
# AuthMechs XOAUTH2

IMAPStore gmail-private-remote
Account gmail-private

MaildirStore gmail-private-local
Path ~/documents/mail/gmail-private/
Inbox ~/documents/mail/gmail-private/INBOX
SubFolders verbatim

Channel gmail-private
Far :gmail-private-remote:
Near :gmail-private-local:
Patterns *
Expunge Near
CopyArrivalDate yes
Sync Full
Create Near
SyncState *
